# Nata.House Create React Home Template

## Useful documentation

You can find more detailed documentation on the [Wiki]() of this project or inside `docs`folder.

## Updates

The boilerplate will follow new ReactJS releases as soon as libraries and tools used here are compatible.

## Requirements

- Node 12 or greater is required.
- Git client

## Running the project

To run the project you just need run this steps:

- Clone this project.
- Install all de dependencies with `yarn` or `npm`
- Run the command `yarn start` or `npm run start`
